@page "/about"

<div class="container-fluid p-0" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background: #fff8e1; min-height: 100vh; position: relative;">
    <!-- Back to Home Button -->
    <a class="btn btn-outline-primary" href="/" style="position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 20px; border-radius: 25px;">
        Back to Home
    </a>

    <!-- Page Title -->
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4" style="color: #333;">About Us</h1>

        <!-- Content Section -->
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-10">
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #555;">
                    At <strong>Paws & Claws</strong>, we believe in the magic of companionship. Pets are not just animals; they are family members who bring love, laughter, and unforgettable moments into our lives. From wagging tails to gentle purrs, their presence fills our homes with joy and unconditional affection. Our mission is simple yet powerful: to create meaningful connections between pets and people, ensuring that every animal finds a warm, loving home and every family discovers the perfect addition to their lives.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #555;">
                    Founded on the principles of compassion and care, Paws & Claws has become a trusted name in pet adoption. We work tirelessly with local shelters, breeders, and rescue organizations to provide a wide range of pets, each waiting for their forever family. Our team is dedicated to making the adoption process smooth, transparent, and heartwarming. Whether you’re adopting your first pet or welcoming a new friend to your family, we’re here to guide you every step of the way.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #555;">
                    Beyond pet adoption, we are passionate about creating a supportive community for pet lovers. Through workshops, events, and resources, we empower families with the knowledge and tools needed to care for their furry companions. From training tips to health advice, our commitment doesn’t end when you bring your new friend home—it’s a lifelong journey of support and care. Together, we build stronger bonds, ensuring that every pet and owner shares a fulfilling and joyful life.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #555;">
                    Paws & Claws is more than just an organization; it’s a movement to celebrate the beauty of human-animal connections. Every adoption is a story of hope, and every pet is a testament to resilience and love. Join us in our mission to transform lives, one paw at a time. Together, let’s create a world where every pet has a home, and every home is filled with the boundless love of a furry friend.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
